  "description": "2D key-move dungeon-crawl board FRAME: composes hero-nav (key-move intent) + dungeon-combat (bump-attack, monster chase, hero HP) + objective-reach (exit/chest) + fx-particles + objective-flow (win) onto one shared GameState with a canvas-2d render. Games consume this molecule and supply only theme/assets/tiles/units/enemies/features via config.",
